title: SharePoint Training
description: Mindmajix offers the best SharePoint training that helps the learners leverage the SharePoint environment through an innovative and experimental learning platform. It includes the SharePoint fundamentals like SharePoint server architecture, SharePoint server installation, SharePoint high-level elements, creating workspaces, and handling form libraries. Our live project work and practical assignments offer you an in-depth understanding of custom alerts, access levels, custom sites, Infopath, custom templates, database templates, and Sites customization.  Along with these, trainees will also master SharePoint API, SharePoint workflows, and SharePoint Administration. Join our SharePoint online training to position yourself well in the market.
